00:09:04,995 --> 00:09:06,940
That's exactly what we're going to figure out!

574
00:09:07,269 --> 00:09:08,510
Today is the sixteenth,

1446
00:09:08,605 --> 00:09:10,586
so that gives us eight days to get ready

1547
00:09:10,610 --> 00:09:12,745
for the plan all the fun we're gonna have!

1733
00:09:12,894 --> 00:09:15,326
Anyway, I went ahead and picked up some stuff.

278
00:09:15,350 --> 00:09:16,089
Check it out!

2015
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:18,376
This will help everyone get into the Christmas spirit

2051
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:21,120
and make this party the coolest thing we've ever done!

782
00:09:21,230 --> 00:09:23,167
Oh, great, more knick-knacks!

1198
00:09:23,260 --> 00:09:25,260
Where did she find that junk anyway?

823
00:09:25,394 --> 00:09:26,446
This will help brighten up our

1447
00:09:26,470 --> 00:09:29,011
drab little club room like never before!

1773
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:32,823
Didn't you used to do this when you were a kid?

1264
00:09:33,210 --> 00:09:35,089
Yeah, well, I never really wanted to,

1139
00:09:35,114 --> 00:09:36,634
but every year I was forced to help

1774
00:09:36,670 --> 00:09:38,886
my little sister get her room all Christmas-up.

1199
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:40,586
Even though she is eleven years old,

1064
00:09:40,610 --> 00:09:42,253
