2113
00:09:42,280 --> 00:09:44,670
And it looks I'll have to do it again for her this year.

1548
00:09:44,792 --> 00:09:48,144
You know, you could learn a lot from
your kid sister's pure and innocent heart.

1320
00:09:48,310 --> 00:09:51,370
You have to believe in a dream if
you wanna have one in the first place.

942
00:09:51,590 --> 00:09:54,839
If you don't believe, even the
dreams that can come true won't!

550
00:10:03,260 --> 00:10:04,815
