1065
00:10:05,565 --> 00:10:07,530
When in Rome, do as the Romans do.

1321
00:10:07,670 --> 00:10:11,815
When it's Christmas, it's only logical
that we follow the rules of Christmas!

1448
00:10:12,170 --> 00:10:15,980
Getting into the vibe is gonna be easy,
'cause everybody likes birthday parties.

1322
00:10:16,590 --> 00:10:20,836
