but I know I don't have to go
back there right now, either.

2140
02:36:02,920 --> 02:36:06,481
You got that, world? You're okay for a bit there, right?

1899
02:36:06,996 --> 02:36:11,340
You don't mind if I take a little break
before going back in time and fixing you, do you?

188
02:36:12,010 --> 02:36:13,129
Oh, well.

1382
02:36:15,260 --> 02:36:19,559
At least, wait until after I have
some of Haruhi's hotpot cooking, okay?

275
02:41:13,063 --> 02:41:14,083
There. Done.

225
02:41:14,220 --> 02:41:15,340
Thank you.

94
02:41:19,970 --> 02:41:20,690
Here.

53
02:41:20,860 --> 02:41:21,540
Wow.

166
02:41:23,300 --> 02:41:24,110
Come on!

95
